      "effect": "You can activate \"Metalmorph\" Trap Cards the turn they are Set. You can only use each of the following effects of \"Red-Eyes Metal Claw Dragon\" once per turn. You can send 1 face-down card you control to the GY; Special Summon this card from your hand. If this card is Normal or Special Summoned, and you have \"Max Metalmorph\" in your field or GY: You can add 1 \"Metalmorph\" Trap from your Deck or GY to your hand.",
